Author: Roy Gusinow [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Roy Gusinow <rgusinow@uni-bonn.de>
Description: Tools for federated matching and estimation of average treatment
    effects (ATE, ATT, and ATC) using DataSHIELD. The package includes robust
    variance estimators, diagnostics, and matching-based summary plots.
